title: **Beautiful Luxury Apartment** MOVE IN NOW!! 1 BEDROOM
posting_body: ['At the heart of the Mile High City, This large glass-sided sky pool offers the cityscape an iconic wow factor—eight stories into the sky.', 'Residents of this landmark property situated in Denver’s Central Business District, revel in the luxury of artful studio, one-, and two-bedroom apartment homes and penthouse residences.', 'Amenties:', '-Glass-sided pool with skyline views', '-Private parking', '-24-hour concierge', '-Conveniences including parcel and cold storage and AliceHome premium services to help manage in-home tasks', '-The Quincy Black Card, an access pass to exclusive perks and local discounts', '-Indoor-outdoor fitness center and movement studio', '-Alfresco kitchen, BBQ area and fire pits', '-Resident lounge with entertainment kitchen and gaming center', '-Business center and coffee lounge', '-Shareable E-bikes', '-Pet friendly with pet spa', '-Private, secured resident storage', 'Call or Text Tyler to set up your for Fast Personal Showings or Virtual Showings!', '*Restrictions Apply.', 'Pricing, availability and lease terms subject to change anytime!']
